    <h3  class="f4-mktg color-fg-muted pb-2" aria-hidden="true"> The Hartford</h3>
    <p  class="h6-mktg color-fg-default py-1 pb-sm-4 text-semibold" aria-hidden="true">Through collaboration and innersourcing, The Hartford uses GitHub to evolve into a customer-centric insurance company.</p>
    <p class="f4 d-block d-sm-inline no-underline text-semibold arrow-target-mktg color-fg-accent" aria-hidden="true">
