    <h3  class="f4-mktg color-fg-muted pb-2" aria-hidden="true"> Jibo, Inc.</h3>
    <p  class="h6-mktg color-fg-default py-1 pb-sm-4 text-semibold" aria-hidden="true">Jibo, the social robot, is brought to life by developers all over the world. See how these builders connect with the core team on GitHub.</p>
