    <h3  class="f4-mktg color-fg-muted pb-2" aria-hidden="true"> XING</h3>
    <p  class="h6-mktg color-fg-default py-1 pb-sm-4 text-semibold" aria-hidden="true">XING integrates open and closed source code to build collaborative workflows everyone can use—from project planning to QA.</p>
